HEADWORD: Sericin
<hw>Ser"i*cin</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>sericus</ets> silken.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A gelatinous
